Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.32,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:45.66,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.67,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:57.59,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:02.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:05.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.77,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:12.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.90,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:23.16,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:28.87,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:32.09,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:32.92,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:36.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:42.05,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:48.94,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.48,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.11,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.82,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.28,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
